Makkah - Public Relations/Media Coordinator
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 13:19:00
Ref. JB3046962
Job Description
Reporting to Public Relations Manager, successful candidate will be responsible to coordinate with different medias and stake holders in public welfare offices, like local government, municipality, electrical company, etc.
Skills
Bachelor in Communication, Business Administration or equavalent and at least 2-3 years experience in specific job. Shoud have good knowledge of media and offices related softwares. Must be a Saudi national.
Education
Buiseness Administration, Communication, Media
